=== Router: literal / param / wildcard dispatch ===

GET /posts/42
  status: 200
  body:   {"post_id":"42","via_request_params":"42"}

GET /posts/new  (literal beats :id)
  status: 200
  body:   <form>new post</form>

GET /files/css/site.css  (wildcard splat)
  status: 200
  body:   serving: css/site.css

GET /api/echo?user=ada&tags[]=x&tags[]=y  (nested params)
  status: 200
  body:   {"user":"ada","tags":["x","y"]}

GET /nowhere
  status: 404
  body:   Not Found

=== Session cookie round-trip ===

1st GET /  -> <html><body><h1>Rack on rubylang</h1><p>Visits: 1</p></body></html>
   Set-Cookie present: true
2nd GET /  (replaying cookie) -> <html><body><h1>Rack on rubylang</h1><p>Visits: 2</p></body></html>
3rd GET /  (forged cookie, signature rejected) -> <html><body><h1>Rack on rubylang</h1><p>Visits: 1</p></body></html>

=== Rack::Static serving a file ===

GET /hello.txt
  status:       200
  content-type: text/plain
  body:         "a static asset\n"

GET /does-not-exist.png
  status: 404

